// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SwiftCut 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro2 Text :
"P3458327779" "Thank you for your timely arrival, {HeroName}. I believe we have to speak about your proper payment, correct?"
// Answer Text :
"P76181392" "That's right - including this initial rescue fee, which wasn't planned."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P28976046" "Ah...that is correct. <br><br>I suppose I will have that added to my 'tab' as it were..."
// Answer Text :
"P2666013413" "Right. I'll need half now, and half when the job is done."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P2616934824" "H-half now? Is this...really an appropriate time for that?"
// Answer Text :
"P4137175099" "It's how it works, Swift Cut."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1022624814" "<color orange>Swift Cut pulls out a credit card and hands it to you.</color><br><br>This will give you access to my bank account - you can take all of the funds out of it. Most of it is blood money, anyway.<br><br><color orange>Swift Cut sighs, looking up towards the ceiling.</color><br><br>Money from countless deaths...how many have I-"
// Answer Text :
"P1913727032" "Excuse me, Swift Cut?"
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P2119880432" "Er...yes?"
// Answer Text :
"P697981259" "Listening to your backstory will cost extra. Time is money, you know."
// Page Backstory Text :
"P352616400" "<color orange>Swift Cut blinks.</color><br><br>...okay. There's one straight route out of here, but it will be filled with enemies from the Whispering Hand."
// Answer Text :
"P36467029" "Not a problem. Let's get moving."
// Page FirstAmbush Text :
"P4206583780" "We need to keep moving!"
// Answer Text :
"P3872068105" "Tell me something I don't know!"
// Page Disgrace Text :
"P1651132426" "<color orange>Swift Cut clenches her hand, looking downward, tears appearing in her eyes.</color><br><br>I'm...I'm <i>not</i> a disgrace to my family...I'm NOT! <br><br>You understand, don't you {HeroName}?! About what must be done? To salvage everything from nothing?!"
// Answer Text :
"P3172180782" "...is this going to take a while? We're on a schedule here."
// Page Schedule Text :
"P2391712959" "Do...do you not even care, {HeroName}? About this?"
// Answer Text :
"P2241975110" "Look, you hired me to protect you - and I am. I'm not interested in extra baggage."
// Page Baggage Text :
"P4237941616" "<color orange>Swift Cut sighs, gathering herself.</color><br><br>...very well. You're right. Let's get moving."
// Answer Text :
"P4168097617" "It's about time. Let's go!"
// Page Determined Text :
"P1675298583" "I'm determined to get through this, {HeroName}. No matter what."
// Answer Text :
"P4173687746" "Good. Let's keep moving."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SilentBlade 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3126081067" "You're strong...{HeroName}...I'll give you that. <br><br>So...Swift Cut has hired you out...has she...? I'd like to make you an offer then..."
// Answer Text :
"P506002825" "What kind of offer?"
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3359795622" "You stop everything and leave now...allowing me to deal with Swift Cut...and I shall promise that my Whispering Hands will not <i>track you down and kill you and everyone you care about.</i><br><br>I believe that is fair...correct? As you have meddled...<i>much</i> too far into our affairs."
// Answer Text :
"P1241011789" "Look, Silent Blade. Don't make this personal. This is just business, alright?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P362593426" "Hmph. Business? Then my proposition is just 'business'."
// Answer Text :
"P3287992602" "Well, then I have one thing to say to that."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1022904143" "Oh do you now?"
// Answer Text :
"P3052707147" "Good luck."
// Page Luck Text :
"P902929698" "<color orange>Silent Blade glares at you before vanishing in a flash!</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2273603948" "Let's keep moving..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - SilentBlade2 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro2 Text :
"P1512797305" "<color orange>Silent Blade lays on the ground, having succumbed to the injuries of the two fights with you.</color><br><br>....tell me...{HeroName}...the feeling of...not having responsibility. For your actions...for what you do...tell me...how does it feel...?"
// Answer Text :
"P2569196795" "Look, are we done here? I don't have time for this."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1162283006" "I only...I only wanted to protect my sister...even if it was from...herself...that item she holds...is an evil artifact...<br><br>...if she is to...leave with it...it would mean the doom...of us all...!."
// Answer Text :
"P3978670711" "Right, sure, of course. Are you not getting that this isn't my problem?"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P332164002" "<color orange>Swift Cut walks over, placing a small statue at Silent Blade's feet.</color><br><br>...Father's...final letter to me? Inside of this statue?"
// Answer Text :
"P1806989795" "(Look over) The submarine is here, Swift Cut. Now get going!"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3318032741" "<color orange>Swift Cut leaps into the submarine, which quickly submerges back underneath the water. You turn to Silent Blade, who has the small statue in her hands.</color><br><br>So...I suppose this is where you finish me off, isn't it?"
// Answer Text :
"P290426409" "My job here is done - finishing you off now isn't part of any deal."
// Page Deal Text :
"P2141458830" "<color orange>Silent Blade lets out a laugh.</color><br><br>Just like that...huh...you're able to just walk away from it...an...admirable trait...<br><br>Perhaps...it is not too late then...for myself to turn away..."
// Answer Text :
"P1528084944" "Whatever you say. (Leave)"
// Page Firstambush Text :
"P281416701" "<color orange>Silent Blade ignores you as she reads over a piece of paper she has removed from the statue.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1075424845" "(Leave her be)"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3784012960" "You send a message back to Swift Cut saying that you're in on the deal, along with stating how much money you'll be requiring from her for the job to be done. <br><br>She contacts you shortly afterwards, informing you that she has already begun to make her way into the sewers, thinking you would not show up - however she has run into the Whispering Hand and is currently on the run from them! <br><br>She has found somewhere to hide for now, but will not last very long with the group on her tail. "
// AcceptString :
"P4270250290" "Rescue Swift Cut and get her to Faultline!"
// SendOffString :
"P539350731" "You tell Swift Cut to stay where she is, saying that you'll be there right away. <br><br>You'll have to hurry before the Whispering Hand gets her - once that happens, you can say goodbye to your payday!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P478846941" "Get Swift Cut into Paragon City!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1697386993" "No one has any patience in this town anymore."
// TaskTitle :
"P914990095" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Playing the Sides</color></span></scale></font>"
// TaskSubTitle :
"P292316059" "<span align=center><color orange><i>Rogue Morality Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3302853994" "You've made your way into the sewers beneath Paragon City - why exactly Swift Cut decided to use this path is beyond you, but that doesn't matter right now. <br><br>You see up ahead that Swift Cut is surrounded - looks like members of the Tsoo are being used as the footsoldiers for the Whispering Hand!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2666398835" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Playing the Sides</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Morality Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You return to the Isles with Swift Cut's credit card - a quick check shows that all of the money you required for your payment is within the account specified here. <br><br>What happens next between her and Silent Blade is none of your concern - unless, of course, it leads to a future job. <br><br>Then you'll be all ears for what has to be done."

