// SaysList :
"P213354124" "That was close. We should keep an eye out for more..."
// SaysList :
"P2898967084" "I think...we're good. Right?"
// SaysList :
"P544262573" "I never wanted to be part of this! <em t=2>No one ever asked me! No one!"
// SaysList :
"P597241693" "This isn't justice! You're blind!"
// SaysList :
"P975446163" "Metsuo...I'm sorry it had to be like this..."
// SaysList :
"P2661805641" "Silent Blade must never see it! I refuse!"
// SaysList :
"P1070611370" "I didn't want it to be like this..."
// SaysList :
"P1536805271" "Family? This isn't about family...not anymore. Not after what happened. <em t=3>{HeroName}...I...I need a moment..."
// SaysList :
"P2805093524" "She knows nothing of forgiveness anymore! You and I both realize that!<em t=2>You don't have to do this.  We had good times together. It can be different!"
// SaysList :
"P2863638950" "Let's...let's go, {HeroName}...I just...I just wanted to get out of these sewers...<em t=2>We're almost there...!"
// SaysList :
"P1477739027" "{HeroName} has been hired to protect me...{Hero.gender=male he|she} won't let you kill me...!"
// SaysList :
"P4249872577" "Don't listen to her, {HeroName}! She's just using you, like all the others!"
// SaysList :
"P75548513" "That...was close. Now we just need to signal for the submarine and I will be home free!<em t=2>...well, as close to a new 'home' as Paragon will ever get."
// SaysList :
"P2959433537" "Now we just need to stay alive until the submarine arrives...!"
// SaysList :
"P3085002796" "I think...I think we're almost out of - <em t=2>Silent Blade...!"
// SaysList :
"P4868236" "You have no right to call me 'sister'! You were NEVER there for me, 'big sister'! You used me for your own ends!"
// SaysList :
"P1658722535" "WAIT! {HeroName}, don't kill her! Please...!"
// SaysList :
"P3655969179" "I told you it was evil because...this is something you shouldn't see, sister...please...just let me go."
// SaysList :
"P2385801054" "I was afraid if you read this...you would not be able to handle it. <em t=2>I...know I could not. Which is why I finally chose to flee."
// SaysList :
"P2663589759" "Yes...goodbye {HeroName}. Thank you for everything..."

